title: [Rozy's Magic Shoppe]
[Rozy's General Store]
[Rozy's Weaponry]
description: White silk-paneled walls rise from a swirled sea glass floor.  Just above a mound of silk-covered pillows hangs a peacock feather fan, and a billowing silk ceiling completes the picture.  A beveled glass-covered case and a low wrought iron table stand side by side in the middle of the room.
